{"tid":1610622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔好比狗方spin走嚴重性！！那是「行刑」。","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T20:40:14.000Z","uid":303614,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"68b8a267c318ae6e52a527add46eb72781a8e232","tid":1610622,"uid":303614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:30:19.000Z","msg":"轉自FB<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>《行刑》<br />\n<br />\n那不是「拯救自己及同袍生命」、不是「自衛」、不是「意外」、不是「迫不得已」、甚至不是「意圖謀殺」。<br />\n<br />\n那是「行刑」。<br />\n<br />\nClose range，朝胸口開火 &mdash;&mdash; 這是鎗斃式「行刑」才會做的事。<br />\n<br />\n#用字很重要<br />\n#不要被人牽著鼻子走<br />\n<br />\n#從今以後<br />\n#我們會緊記十月一日的意義<br />\n#直至最後一個香港人<br />\n#嚥下最後一口氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alfredlgj?__tn__=%2CdCH-R-R&amp;eid=ARDvcwdouEeR1aGQ3JdvEALMYuZ6gkrqIBiykfJ1e2kmmjxqxITqC1OeLDTZFV9ufamgtor_QwSaUs-e&amp;hc_ref=ARTHzbSwKJSGoCWd7igX4jFAOKK0tTZwkUpLA7fLNmdejPEIhEmTNvdhFDYxGIXkHg4&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falfredlgj%3F__tn__%3D%252CdCH-R-R%26eid%3DARDvcwdouEeR1aGQ3JdvEALMYuZ6gkrqIBiykfJ1e2kmmjxqxITqC1OeLDTZFV9ufamgtor_QwSaUs-e%26hc_ref%3DARTHzbSwKJSGoCWd7igX4jFAOKK0tTZwkUpLA7fLNmdejPEIhEmTNvdhFDYxGIXkHg4%26fref%3Dnf&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=4fac3329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/alfredlgj?__tn__=%2CdCH-R-R&amp;eid=ARDvcwdouEeR1aGQ3JdvEALMYuZ6gkrqIBiykfJ1e2kmmjxqxITqC1OeLDTZFV9ufamgtor_QwSaUs-e&amp;hc_ref=ARTHzbSwKJSGoCWd7igX4jFAOKK0tTZwkUpLA7fLNmdejPEIhEmTNvdhFDYxGIXkHg4&amp;fref=nf</a>"},{"pid":"24575b41c413ba1aac6391882f96bf049f157820","tid":1610622,"uid":67043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:15:02.000Z","msg":"啱....係行刑式開槍"},{"pid":"cecb4f7263f4c7d0b3da5f2dae4a9ab4378266cb","tid":1610622,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:20:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3243444099016115/\"